    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;ve never been to Chez Panisse, though it&#39;s a dream of mine to eat there. Reading your profile, it struck me that Alice Waters seems so gracious and fierce at the same time. What an inspiring way to live. Alice Waters is an icon in so many ways- I think it&#39;s fitting that you, whose writing is gracious and sometimes quietly radical, were chosen to write about her. Thanks to you both for your important work. </p>
    </div>

