      <p>Alice Waters is an inspiration. I worked for a few years as the Chairperson for the Wellness Council for our school district here in California (by law school districts have to have this committee here) trying, sometimes vainly, to institute something even close to what Alice has done in her school garden program. Your writing (which inspired me to write a blog!), combined with her inspiration, is special indeed. It&#39;s reminded me why I started cooking in the first place (and that I&#39;m sometimes busier than I used to be so I&#39;m not doing it as much as I once did &#8211; or not as passionately, anyway!) Note to self to fix that.</p>
